🛠️ Installation

1) Install dependencies
`
pip install fastapi uvicorn sqlalchemy pydantic transformers torch
`

2) Run the API server
`
uvicorn app.main:app --reload
`

3) Open API docs
بعد التشغيل افتح:

`
http://127.0.0.1:8000/docs (127.0.0.1 in Bing)
`

---

🧪 Testing the API

Build cognitive model
`
POST /api/v1/cognitive-model/rebuild/{student_id}
`

Predict error
`
POST /api/v1/error-prediction/
`

Generate adaptive path
`
GET /api/v1/adaptive-path/{student_id}
`

Track growth
`
GET /api/v1/growth-tracker/{student_id}
`

Detect affect
`
POST /api/v1/affect-detector/
`

